Meta.DockerRequired=False
Meta.ContainerPolicy=SupportedOnWindows, RecommendedOnLinux
Meta.ContainerPolicyReason=The server requires Wine (ideally latest stable from winehq.org) and the VC++ 2015-2022 runtime to run on Linux. Using a container avoids the need for you to install these dependencies on the host.
